Majestic vaulted ceilings, open kitchen with SS appliances, family room, formal living and dinning rooms. Brand new A/C. Very bright with the perfect (split bedrooms) layout. Master bedroom/bathroom with ample storage and closets. Lush backyard, with fruit trees, perfect for entertainment and relaxation.This is a very quiet neighborhood and a superb school district, close to major super markets, stores, banks, great restaurants, etc.
